data.description: Charming 1,509 sq ft rambler style home with three bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom, situated on a spacious Nearly a half acre lot. Enjoy privacy with a fully fenced yard and a detached two car garage. The home features an electric furnace and a shared driveway for convenience. Relax in the hot tub or make use of the outbuildings and greenhouse for your hobbies. The property boasts an individual well and is a great commuter location, just a short distance to the Southworth ferry. Affordable price and a Motivated seller.
